s every 8 hours based on the premium between perpetual and spot prices. Long positions pay short positions when rates are positive, typically during bullish Bitcoin layer-2 sentiment. The exchange applies a ±0.05% funding rate cap with automatic position adjustments. Funding payments occur at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC, with rates visible 1 hour before settlement."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
